Function Description <code>eq</code>, <code>ne</code> Equal, not equal. <code>eq</code> accepts multiple arguments: <code>eq a b c</code> is true if <code>a == b || a == c</code>. <code>lt</code>, <code>le</code>, <code>gt</code>, <code>ge</code> Less-than, less-or-equal, greater-than, greater-or-equal. <code>and</code>, <code>or</code>, <code>not</code> Logical operators. <code>and</code> / <code>or</code> short-circuit and return the first non-empty / non-zero argument. <p>Example:</p> <pre><code>{{if and (eq .Event "upload") (gt .FileSize 1048576) }}
  Large file uploaded by {{.Name}}
{{end}}
</code></pre>
